        <briefdescription>
<para>Validate and balance material item data. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Performs comprehensive validation and balancing on a material item:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Normalizes ID prefix to &quot;Material_&quot;</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Clamps material properties to valid ranges (hardness, flammability, value: 0-100)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Validates material type</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Balances rarity based on item stats</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Generates default description if empty</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="inout">item</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Material item to validate and balance (modified in-place)</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>This function modifies the item parameter directly </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Values are clamped to valid ranges automatically </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
